        public boolean isIs_new_auxiliary_entity()
        Indicate if the new value is the subject of a new auxiliary entity. You must set it to true if you are creating a new auxiliary entity. If it is a new auxiliary entity, you must send the rdf:type and rdfs:label triples too.

        True if the new value is the subject of a new auxiliary entity.
